* Fix release version

3.2.0 - 2024-01-30
******************
* Remove audit access to chat view.

3.0.1 - 2024-01-29
******************
* Modify gating of learning assistant based on waffle flag and enabled value.

3.0.0 - 2024-01-23
******************
* Remove and drop the course prompt model.

